IF NOT EXISTS ( SELECT  *
                FROM    sys.schemas
                WHERE   name = 'miPINS' )
    EXEC('CREATE SCHEMA [miPINS]');
GO


CREATE OR ALTER VIEW miPINS.vw_mipins_listed_building
AS

SELECT DISTINCT
LB.ListedBuildingEntity                 AS ListedBuildingEntity,
LB.ListedBuildingEntryDate              AS ListedBuildingEntryDate,
LB.ListedBuildingName                   AS ListedBuildingName,
LB.ListedBuildingOrganisationEntity     AS ListedBuildingOrganisationEntity,
LB.ListedBuildingPrefix                 AS ListedBuildingPrefix,
LB.ListedBuildingPoint                  AS ListedBuildingPoint,
LB.ListedBuildingReference              AS ListedBuildingReference,
LB.ListedBuildingStartDate              AS ListedBuildingStartDate,
LB.ListedBuildingTypology               AS ListedBuildingTypology,
LB.ListedBuildingDocumentation          AS ListedBuildingDocumentation,
LB.ListedBuildingNumber                 AS ListedBuildingNumber,
LB.ListedBuildingGrade                  AS ListedBuildingGrade


FROM [odw_harmonised_db].[dbo].[listed_building_dim] AS LB

GO
